reviewText: The movies are in great condition!
It was a gift for my sister. She loved it.
My teen has watched it so much I mean need to get a 2nd one
Awesome set of 3 great Martin Lawrence films. All 3 are classics, Bad Boys 2 is better than the 1st but still good to have.

Blue Streak is the gem of this collection. The other two films are very fun but Blue Streak is what makes this a must buy. If you love Martin Lawrence, then jump on this!! What are you waiting for? :P
